import React, { Component } from 'react'
import { Form, FormGroup, Input, Col, Label, FormText,
    Button} from 'reactstrap';



export default class Sign extends Component {
  
  render() {
    return (
         
         <Form style={{
  width: '650px',
  height: '827px',
  backgroundColor: '#ffffff'

         }}>
        <FormGroup>
        <Label style={{color:'#506355', lineHeight:'1.41',
        fontFamily:'roboto',
        fontSize:'36px', fontWeight:'500',
        textAlign:'center', marginTop:'40px'}}>
            Sign In
        </Label>
       </FormGroup>  
        <FormGroup row>
        
         <Col sm={10}>
            <Input 
            style ={{backgroundColor:'#ffffff', color:'#c4c4c4',
            borderRadius:'3px', height: '65px', width:'589px',
            border:'solid 2px #c4c4c4', fontSize:'24px', color:'c4c4c4',
            lineHeight:'1.41'
            }}
            type="email" name="email" id="exampleEmail"
            placeholder="Email" />
          </Col>
        </FormGroup>
        <FormGroup row>
          <Col sm={10}>
            <Input 
                        style ={{backgroundColor:'#ffffff', color:'#c4c4c4',
                        borderRadius:'3px', height: '65px', width:'589px',
                        border:'solid 2px #c4c4c4', fontSize:'24px', color:'c4c4c4',
                        lineHeight:'1.41'}}

            type="password" name="password" id="examplePassword" placeholder="Password " />
          </Col>
        </FormGroup>
        
        
        <FormGroup row>
               <Col sm={{ size: 10 }}>
            <FormGroup check>
              <Label check>
                <Input 
                style={{width:'25px', height:'25px'}}
                type="checkbox" id="checkbox2" />{' '}
                Remember Me
              </Label>
              <Button style={{backgroundColor:'tranpsaran', marginLeft:'70px'}}>Forget Password</Button>
            </FormGroup>
          </Col>
        </FormGroup>
        <FormGroup check row>
          <Col sm={{ size: 10, offset: 2 }}>
            <Button >Sign In</Button>
          </Col>
        </FormGroup>
      </Form>

    )
  }
}
